  "body": "Type: **Bug**\r\n\r\nSummary: Text of message is not formatted accordingly in a reply frame when message in chat (1-1 / group / public) was sent wrapped up with asterisks (*) or tildes (~)\r\n\r\n**Expected behaviour**\r\n\r\nText of message in a reply bubble in bold/italic font is displayed in a specific selected style\r\n\r\n**Actual behaviour**\r\n\r\nText of message in a reply bubble in bold/italic font is displayed with asterisks (*) or tildes (~), not formatted\r\n\r\n<img width=\"709\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/43638377/48420316-ca33be00-e762-11e8-9f6d-07758096e846.png\">\r\n \r\n**Reproduction**\r\n\r\n1. Open Status\r\n2. Start 1-1 chat/public chat\r\n3. Send message wrapped up with asterisks and tyldes (e.g. *Bold*, ~Italic~ fonts)\r\n4. Reply to that message and check out how it's displayed in the reply bubble\r\n\r\n**Additional Information**\r\n\r\nStatus version: Develop (d2160e) \r\nOperating System: iOS 12.0, MacOS 10.13.4",
